governance is an question open for public discussion.

# hive proposals

proposals can be submitted to hives.

## parties involved

all members of the hive

## process involved

spectrum of possibilities:

- consensus only, everyone must agree
- all but n consensus
- percent agreement
- supermajority in favor
- majority in favor
- largest minority

# hive bank

the hive must keep inventory of its existing resources and accept incoming resources.

## parties involved

hive bank admins
hive members

## error checking

all members of the hive can submit proposals to hive bank as a form of bug reporting
